prompt:
Review this proposed architecture decision:
Title: {title}
Context: {context}
Proposed solution: {solution}
Alternatives considered: {alternatives}

Challenge this ADR by:
1. Identifying unstated assumptions
2. Stress-testing with 10x scale, team turnover, and 'what if we're wrong' scenarios
3. Evaluating operational complexity (who pages at 3am for this?)
4. Checking for reversibility — how painful is it to change course in 18 months?
5. Suggesting what we should prototype or time-box before committing
6. Rating: strong yes, conditional yes (with what conditions), or hold (and why)
